title: Revisiting this project to include tracking for all the bus routes displayed on…
message: Revisiting this project to include tracking for all the bus routes displayed on the METRO Real Time Map.  Due to the functionality of the app changing, I changed the name to "Cincinnati Bus and Streetcar Map". I moved the Map display to it's own activity, added a list to select the route, added comments, and cleaned up some of the constants.
